Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.78,0:01:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離愛麗絲的誕生只剩下一點點時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.13,0:01:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:44.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親…大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:48.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金絲雀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.18,0:01:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你是「父親大人」…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.74,0:02:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅真不是只會去見愛麗絲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為什麼不去實現  你們所深愛著的父親大人的願望呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.62,0:02:17.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行愛麗絲遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.29,0:02:18.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  父親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:23.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:43.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  明日早晨  在n之領域恭候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.92,0:03:04.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會有這種事呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:08.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人竟然和薔薇水晶在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.46,0:03:10.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼樣都無所謂的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只能去戰鬥了的說了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為什麼要聽從那種傢伙的命令啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.50,0:03:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已經完全想清楚了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.54,0:03:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了取回蒼星石的薔薇聖母
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.22,0:03:28.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能夠逃避愛麗絲遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.63,0:03:32.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會！一定還有其他方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.82,0:03:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？這  這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留下來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為  為什麼呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.86,0:03:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:47.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶你過去到處亂跑也只會妨礙我們的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:49.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我希望你可不要把我當作傻瓜吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:52.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種沒半點威力的小提琴演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.81,0:03:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒用的說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧？撥弦！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想喝紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純  你沒聽到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅茶…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:32.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說過你不會戰鬥嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.82,0:04:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅  還有翠星石都說過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…竟然是羅真…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.73,0:04:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你見過父親大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算見過他也什麼都改變不了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.39,0:05:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等於是什麼都不知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.56,0:05:06.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  什麼都做不到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.57,0:05:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能和我一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雛莓把她的薔薇聖母托付給了真紅的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:50.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今往後都會和真紅在一起的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.41,0:06:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼星石以後也要一直一直和翠星石在一起的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金  快看快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:14.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前拍的照片我做成海報了哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.30,0:06:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  你看你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.96,0:06:19.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～大家都太可愛了～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金和小雛的合照  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:23.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做成超大版的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要釘在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:27.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對了  一定要買個畫框才行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用圖釘釘在牆上實在是太可惜了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後掛在哪裡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在正中間…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.33,0:07:42.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  早飯好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:46.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:49.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就吃…花蛋漢堡扒…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我必須走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天有練習比賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.67,0:08:01.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯我會做更加更加好吃的的東西哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:03.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點…回來哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.99,0:08:13.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那麼  我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紀…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來人啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:29.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：{\fnふみゴシック\fe128}賴もう{\r}，是日本古代去道場踢館時叫門用的話）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.57,0:08:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個聲音是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.13,0:08:32.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金絲雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明叫你不要來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:37.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不懂事的傢伙的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.81,0:08:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金絲雀不來的話  愛麗絲遊戲就沒辦法開始吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.83,0:08:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說我也是薔薇少女中第一軍師…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.41,0:08:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是碰到危險就夾起尾巴趕快逃跑的說哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.21,0:08:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.02,0:09:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.14,0:09:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.29,0:09:42.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.35,0:09:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅  羅真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.42,0:09:53.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請聽我說！父親大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.56,0:09:55.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不想戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然對父親大人的決定有異議…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.04,0:10:00.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法原諒你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.78,0:10:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:13.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.22,0:10:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要取回蒼星石的薔薇聖母的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒真紅之前  再拿一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.22,0:10:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小金也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.10,0:10:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了吧？野薔薇之前奏曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:15.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？完全沒有用嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.03,0:11:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:21.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二章  垂首士兵之進行曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快給我逃遠點的說  金絲雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:41.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:44.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還能援助同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還滿游刃有餘的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水銀燈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.83,0:11:52.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你一個人又能做些什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你在瞄準哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:02.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要拿回蒼星石的薔薇聖母吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.80,0:12:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最重要最重要的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這裡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.91,0:12:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你看個好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.42,0:12:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能用這把剪刀打敗你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.22,0:12:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才盡興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.50,0:12:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.36,0:12:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.84,0:12:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅真！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:01.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅是為了阻止愛麗絲遊戲才到這裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:04.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說  她們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:14.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金的聲音攻擊竟然完全沒有用…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.78,0:13:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就聽真紅的話不來了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？少了一個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.92,0:13:26.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:38.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被…被…被  被粉碎了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.65,0:13:45.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒有看別處的時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:49.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所面對的  可是我水銀燈！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.61,0:13:52.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真  真紅！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:15.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是能找麻煩的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:18.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別在那裡發呆快給我過來的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.39,0:14:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.79,0:14:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你打算做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.76,0:14:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快從門那裡逃跑的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不知道能擋住她多久
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.14,0:14:31.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我陪你走一段的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:32.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.57,0:14:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小  小金還能戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明就在那裡抱著頭髮抖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:36.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就別囉嗦逞強了的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:47.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想再眼睜睜地  看著誰的薔薇聖母被奪走了的說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.91,0:14:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  抓緊走的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要粉碎了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:31.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要想其它的事情的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去門那裡的說哦！金絲雀！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.39,0:15:36.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了！快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:56.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.51,0:16:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我現在就過去吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的薔薇聖母
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.35,0:16:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.97,0:16:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.51,0:16:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次我來救你吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋！為什麼回來的說啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你也不用這麼說吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:47.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:50.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也就是一次拿兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.79,0:16:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑的說！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.22,0:17:08.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠…翠星…石…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.63,0:17:26.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！你沒聽見嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神聖的愛麗絲遊戲正在向正確的方向進行著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.38,0:17:42.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.89,0:17:52.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來…保護吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想從旁邊搶走…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.32,0:17:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把翠星石的薔薇聖母
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.29,0:18:08.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不給你…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.80,0:18:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:12.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到底有什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太美麗了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.21,0:18:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安靜地燃燒著  憤怒的和歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.77,0:18:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出真本事來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的話  真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:38.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是對翠星石見死不救哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,致失去之時刻的鎮魂曲！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小金能做到的  就只有…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.23,0:18:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要保護吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:14.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要保護翠星石的薔薇聖母！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.10,0:19:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於認真起來了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:39.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石  借給  借給小金力量吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不…不給你吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.51,0:20:14.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石由我  由我來保護吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.52,0:20:17.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要再接近了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.33,0:20:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也做得到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.46,0:20:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次  這次我要為大家派上用場吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.46,0:20:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對  絕對不會把翠星石交給你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:40.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要一定要保護…她…吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.46,0:20:56.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.35,0:21:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不可以…過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.02,0:21:03.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星…石…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.17,0:21:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金  金絲雀…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:36.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.75,0:23:44.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那個時候開始  我就一直在祈求著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.74,0:23:47.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈求那唯一的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.74,0:23:50.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直相信著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信那唯一的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.37,0:23:56.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在父親大人的面前  愛麗絲正…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.06,0:24:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  薔薇少女  夢見
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那旋律宛如夢中所見
